### =============================================================
### AlAshmar API - Flow: Generate Daily Report
### =============================================================
###
### This file walks through generating daily reports for:
###   - A specific student
###   - A specific teacher
###   - A specific class (halaqa)
###   - Overall attendance (all students/teachers)
###   - Overall points
###
### Instructions:
###   1. Run Step 1 (Login) first and copy the token.
###   2. Replace the placeholder IDs with real IDs from your DB.
###   3. Run each report request individually.
### =============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5107

# Update these variables with real values:
@authToken  = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@studentId  = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@teacherId  = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000011
@classId    = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000041
# Date format: YYYY-MM-DD  (leave blank to default to today)
@reportDate = 2025-03-15

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# STEP 1 - Authenticate
# -----------------------------------------------------------------

### Step 1: Login
# Copy the returned "token" value into @authToken above.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@1234"
}

###

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# STEP 2 - Student Daily Report
# -----------------------------------------------------------------

### Step 2a: Student daily report (today)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/students/{{studentId}}/daily
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 2b: Student daily report (specific date)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/students/{{studentId}}/daily?date={{reportDate}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 2c: Export student daily report as JSON file
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/students/{{studentId}}/daily/export?date={{reportDate}}&format=json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 2d: Export student daily report as XML file
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/students/{{studentId}}/daily/export?date={{reportDate}}&format=xml
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/xml

###

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# STEP 3 - Teacher Daily Report
# -----------------------------------------------------------------

### Step 3a: Teacher daily report (today)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/teachers/{{teacherId}}/daily
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 3b: Teacher daily report (specific date)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/teachers/{{teacherId}}/daily?date={{reportDate}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# STEP 4 - Class (Halaqa) Daily Report
# -----------------------------------------------------------------

### Step 4a: Class daily report (today)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/classes/{{classId}}/daily
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 4b: Class daily report (specific date)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/classes/{{classId}}/daily?date={{reportDate}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# STEP 5 - Attendance Daily Report (whole academy)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------

### Step 5a: Overall attendance daily report (today)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/attendance/daily
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 5b: Overall attendance daily report (specific date)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/attendance/daily?date={{reportDate}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# STEP 6 - Points Daily Report (whole academy)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------

### Step 6a: Overall points daily report (today)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/points/daily
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Step 6b: Overall points daily report (specific date)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/points/daily?date={{reportDate}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

###
